#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an7.26"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.26:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.26:0.2"
msgid "3. Vajjisattakavagga "
msgstr "3. The Vajji Seven "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 26. Bojjhaṅgasutta → catutthabhikkhuaparibhāgiyasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.26:0.3"
msgid "26. Bojjhaṅgasutta "
msgstr "26. Awakening Factors "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an7.26:1.1"
msgid "“Satta vo, bhikkhave, aparihāniye dhamme desessāmi. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you seven principles that prevent decline. "

msgctxt "an7.26:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha … pe … "
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention … "

msgctxt "an7.26:1.3"
msgid "katame ca, bhikkhave, satta aparihāniyā dhammā? "
msgstr "And what are the seven principles that prevent decline? "

msgctxt "an7.26:1.4"
msgid "Yāvakīvañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhū satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāvessanti; vuddhiyeva, bhikkhave, bhikkhūnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihāni. "
msgstr "As long as the mendicants develop the awakening factor of mindfulness … "

#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an7.26:2.1"
msgid "Yāvakīvañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhū dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāvessanti … pe … "
msgstr "investigation of principles … "

msgctxt "an7.26:2.2"
msgid "vīriyasambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāvessanti … "
msgstr "energy … "

msgctxt "an7.26:2.3"
msgid "pītisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāvessanti … "
msgstr "rapture … "

msgctxt "an7.26:2.4"
msgid "passaddhisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāvessanti … "
msgstr "tranquility … "

msgctxt "an7.26:2.5"
msgid "samādhisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāvessanti … "
msgstr "immersion … "

msgctxt "an7.26:2.6"
msgid "upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāvessanti; vuddhiyeva, bhikkhave, bhikkhūnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihāni. "
msgstr "equanimity, they can expect growth, not decline. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an7.26:3.1"
msgid "Yāvakīvañca, bhikkhave, ime satta aparihāniyā dhammā bhikkhūsu ṭhassanti, imesu ca sattasu aparihāniyesu dhammesu bhikkhū sandississanti; vuddhiyeva, bhikkhave, bhikkhūnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihānī”ti. "
msgstr "As long as these seven principles that prevent decline last among the mendicants, and as long as the mendicants are seen following them, they can expect growth, not decline.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.26:3.2"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
